Package cl.clcert.de

Class ScenarioB

  • java.lang.Object
    • cl.clcert.de.DataExtractor
      • cl.clcert.de.ScenarioB

  • public class ScenarioB
extends DataExtractor
    Class that deals with the scenario in which we request data from the UdeChile beacon, retry for 10 min and if the page is not responding we ask for the Nist beacon to get the data, with the same timestamp used for the trial of the first one.
    Author:
    constanzacsori
